-----Commands-----
cancel - Cancel any existing process
copy_from_user - Copy from other users 
select_train - Select your active training
add - Add a card
list - List your cards
review - Review some topics
erase - Erase
edit - Edit
help - Help and developers contact
settings - Change bot settings
start - Sign in to use the bot
stop - Stop the bot

-----Description-----
A bot to help you learn anything you can put into flashcards! You can add subjects and cards you are learning by using /add or copy flashcards from other users, using /copy_from_user. You can create audio, image or text flashcards. The bot will send these flashcards in the best learning intervals for you to answer! 


-----About-----
A bot to help you learn anything you can put into flashcards!
